layout: default-page.twig
title: 聯絡我們

---

<div id="messages"></div>

<h2>填寫聯絡表單</h2>

<p>
    若主機使用有任何問題，歡迎由此聯絡我們處理。也可由此回報主機濫用或不法行為。
</p>

<form id="contact-us" class="uk-form" enctype="application/x-www-form-urlencoded" action="http://api.skycastle.in/v-2/contact-form" method="post">
    <div class="cl">
        <table width="52%" class="contactff order">
            <tr>
                <td class="fright w90">Email</td>
                <td><input name="author_email" id="api_author_email" type="text" value=""/></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="fright w90">姓名</td>
                <td><input name="author_name" id="api_author_name" type="text" value=""/></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="fright w90">主旨</td>
                <td><input name="subject" id="api_subject" type="text" value=""/></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="fright">訊息</td>
                <td><textarea style="width: 100%; height: 250px;" name="content" id="api_content"></textarea></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="fright">&nbsp;</td>
                <td><br>
                    <b>輸入您所看見的驗證碼</b><br>
                    <br>
                    <img alt="captcha" src="http://api.skycastle.in/captcha" id="captcha-image"><br>
                    <br></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="fright">輸入驗證碼</td>
                <td><input name="captcha" id="api_captcha" type="text" id="api_captcha"/></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="fright">&nbsp;</td>
                <td><span class="fright">
                                <button type="submit" class="button_singup r5 button_r uk-button uk-button-primary">送出</button>
                                </span></td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <p>&nbsp;</p>
    </div>
</form>